post_install() {
cat <<EOT

Note: to patch VMware use the command 'vmware-patch' as root.
You can revert it with 'vmware-unpatch'.

Also, do not forget to add a version such as 2012.09.07 in /etc/arch-release (empty file) if the USBArbitrator fails to start.

EOT
}

post_upgrade() {
  post_install
}